snippet.title: Free Documentary
snippet.description:
We are dedicated to bringing high-class documentaries to you on YouTube. With the latest camera equipment used by well-known filmmakers working for famous production studios. You will see fascinating shots from the deep seas and up in the air, capturing great stories and pictures from everything our beautiful and interesting planet has to offer. 

Enjoy stories about nature, wildlife, culture, people, history and more to come.
